    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. She\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like royalty. You\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish; she looks and drives just like she did the day she rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling and want a ride that\u2019s been truly babied, this is the one. Come by for a coffee and a chat, and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
