    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a literal time capsule where the world outside fades into a whisper. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a preserved masterpiece, radiating a deep, mirror-like luster that captures the golden hour even on a cloudy day. The interior greets you with the intoxicating, rich aroma of untouched leather, while every dial and switch operates with the satisfying, tactile precision of a Swiss watch. On the open road, it doesn't just travel\u2014it glides with a soulful purr, offering a visceral, connected experience that modern cars have traded for cold technology. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine jewel of automotive history, a car that has been cherished like a family heirloom and is now ready to define your next great chapter.",
      "price": 44500.0,
